    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在虹尘吞没城市之前． ． ．成为一名高速奔跑的「骑手」，抢在末日前拯救依布达成为英雄。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/31db5069ef7ea788d4fc30f15c3d25b2.poster.avif?t=1766066103\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/31db5069ef7ea788d4fc30f15c3d25b2.webm?t=1766066103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/31db5069ef7ea788d4fc30f15c3d25b2.mp4?t=1766066103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/768ae6cc2c381d729f2767894576ad30.avif?t=1766066103\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>高速跑酷×动作战斗的无缝串接</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以传统的三线跑道融合敌对势力、招架、连段、壁跑、处决等多种有趣系统，创造兼具观赏性与操作感的全新战斗×跑酷玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/40757af022a06039c7e0243fea8a36bf.avif?t=1766066103\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/c4d4962f5093cacd47664f5adf841134.avif?t=1766066103\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>局外养成</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来更新将带来农场与厨房系统，玩家能自行种植食材并烹调强化自身的料理。战斗、采集与制作构成一个紧密循环，带来更深入的探索节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/7a18fcd5d8e05f6e43d9494c4dc5a3cf.avif?t=1766066103\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>视觉与音乐</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自然与高楼完美融合的美丽都会。让玩家能在这座美丽却随时潜藏杀机的城市中自由飞越、漫游，沉浸于紧迫又壮丽的末世氛围。多张不同风格的地图等着您来探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/d65e28bd17cd5c5c88b99d8c4276b43a.avif?t=1766066103\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>立即加入《虹尘》世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《虹尘》目前正持续调整操作手感与游戏节奏，并强调「玩家回馈是最重要的力量」。欢迎各位骑手们加入虹尘的Discord频道，所有更新都会优先回应试玩玩家的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras/d345737fcfa9e1616f97359700bf321e.avif?t=1766066103\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195730/extras_big/d345737fcfa9e1616f97359700bf321e.avif?t=1766066103 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
